task.summary: Adding a connector to handle cross server actions. Will be shifting towards docker.
Made the connector the one to check if a server is up, instead of having the server itself ping, it will check the database. Appears to be working better.
Connector can now send commands to running servers. Will also auto restart a server if found to be out of date.
Now previous changes should work properly.
Connector has Load balancing. Will start servers if there are none. Additionally, added GlobalChat Command. /gc Will check further.
Connector now properly detects player count on server.
